| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4556 — Recovery Inhibition (ElDorado)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3fecb138-bd42-5fb8-b0d0-26a1731d28df"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
